&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who is VetEvolve?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VetEvolve is a network of veterinary practices built to support the people delivering care and the practices they lead. We combine clinical insight with operational strength to give our teams the support, tools, and structure they need to thrive, without losing what makes each practice unique. We are intentionally focused on growth, not as an end in itself, but as a way to strengthen our practices, expand access to care, and create more opportunities for our teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guided by our values: Care First. Better Together. Grow Forward. Own It. We create an environment where veterinary professionals can do their best work, build meaningful careers, and deliver exceptional care. Growth with intention. Care without compromise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.accpetvet.com/subpage.php?menuChoice=about_30&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Animal Care Center&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;in Pearisburg, Virginia&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;is excited to welcome an experienced full or part time veterinarian to their team! This full-service location has a large, nearby sister hospital in Princeton, West Virginia, recently under&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;new leadership!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Both locations are less than one hour from&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Blacksburg, Virginia&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Animal Care Center Pearisburg:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our Pearisburg location is set up perfectly for an experienced veterinarian who enjoys leading the team as the only doctor on shift. You’ll be well-supported by at least two dedicated, experienced technicians/assistants and a well-trained, engaged client relations team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;While Pearisburg shifts are solo shifts, multiple doctors are just minutes away at our large Princeton location. Our 2 doctor team currently rotates shifts between Princeton and Pearisburg locations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Veterinarians across 2 locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, positive Practice Manager focused on team building and smooth day-to-day operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ultrasound, endoscopy/rhinoscopy unit, laser therapy and laser surgery equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Pearisburg, Virginia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Located less than 30 minutes from Blacksburg, VA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pearisburg is an outdoor enthusiasts dream. The Appalachian Trail is located nearby. Pearisburg prides itself on being a hiker friendly town and enjoys its designation as an AT Trail Community. The north flowing river is nearby with newly renovated boat landing and prime fishing opportunities. Library ranked #2 in the state&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Revitalized downtown area with museums, new shops and restaurants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost of living is 20% lower than the national average. Affordable land with with gorgeous mountain surroundings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pearisburg is ranked as one of the safest communities in Virginia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Ideal Candidate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced small animal veterinarian, comfortable working solo shifts with a nearby team to collaborate with as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open to full or part-time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aligned with our core values – Serve, Evolve, Trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
