&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, 2 doctor team seeking a third doctor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 locations - sister hospital located in Pearisburg, Virginia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customized scheduling opportunities to meet your needs in order to allow a better work life balance - full and part time opportunities available&lt;/li&gt;
