&lt;li&gt;Loyal, compliant clientele. Excellent community reputation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Offering new graduate veterinarians to be apart of our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zxZ-xGpoZywDeE1guNjikTJ3-J2R6xuy/view?usp=sharing&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Support From the Start&lt;/a&gt; program; a customized tailored mentorship program for veterinarians.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
