&lt;li&gt;Quality schools and a revitalized downtown filled with museums, unique shops, and diverse dining. Recognized as the &#39;Best Up-and-Coming&#39; town by WV Living Magazine.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideal for outdoor enthusiasts. Take in the beauty of the mountains, large rivers, lakes and waterfalls via nationally renowned trail systems and state parks.&lt;/li&gt;
