&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hospital Attendant / Evening Cleaning Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Part-Time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monday–Friday: 4:00 PM – 7:30 PM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are a busy, compassionate animal hospital dedicated to providing exceptional care to our patients and clients. We are seeking a dependable and detail-oriented Hospital Attendant to assist with end-of-day cleaning and facility maintenance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Hospital Attendant plays an important role in maintaining a clean, sanitary, and welcoming environment for our patients, clients, and veterinary team. This position focuses primarily on evening cleaning duties and ensuring the hospital is prepared for the next business day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean and disinfect exam rooms, treatment areas, and common spaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sweep and mop floors throughout the hospital&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empty trash and recycling receptacles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean and sanitize restrooms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wipe down counters, doors, windows, and high-touch surfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock supplies as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Launder hospital linens and towels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow hospital safety and infection-control protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other weekly and monthly housekeeping duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable, punctual, and self-motivated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in an animal hospital environment around dogs and cats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stand, walk, bend, lift, and perform physical cleaning tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous cleaning or custodial experience is preferred but not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent part-time schedule&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly and supportive team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to contribute to the health and well-being of animals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive hourly pay based on experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
