&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;job Description for a veterinary assistant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;The Veterinary Assistant supports veterinarians and veterinary technicians in providing care for animals. This role involves assisting in medical procedures, maintaining a clean and safe environment, and enhancing the overall experience for clients and their pets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist veterinarians during examinations and medical procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare animals and equipment for surgery and other procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer medications and vaccinations as directed by the veterinarian.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain cleanliness and organization of the clinic, including sterilization of instruments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide general care and feeding for animals in the clinic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record keeping and updating of patients&#39; medical files.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate clients on basic pet care and post-treatment care instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in handling and restraining animals safely and humanely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in a veterinary or animal care setting is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle animals safely and compassionately.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic understanding of animal behavior and medical terminology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physical stamina to lift and restrain pets of various sizes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and ability to follow instructions precisely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certification as a Veterinary Assistant (preferred but not required).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to Learn More?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to learning about your unique priorities and goals and working together with our local hospital teams to support you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

